Stage 7: Representatives + Anchors
ParameterValueTypeWhy this value_REP_HAC_THRESHOLD0.5FIXEDHAC cut for sub-clustering. 0.5 = 50% cosine distance. Tested: 0.3 over-splits, 0.7 under-splits._ANCHOR_IC_MIN4.0FIXEDIC=4 ≈ 2% of hierarchy (e^{-4}). Below: too broad ("Clinical finding" routes everywhere)._ANCHOR_BFS_DEPTH4FIXED4 hops UP from rep → mid-level ancestors for routing. Fewer: too specific. More: too broad._ANCHOR_IC_MAX_BROAD3.0FIXEDAbsolute safety floor. Reject anchors below IC=3.0 no matter what.
